				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Any class with root and DoT spells can solo in yxxta, in a confined space, via root rotting. Why is this so hard to comprehend? There is no difference in solo power between Root+Dots and 100snare+Nukes, provided the DoT spell contains no DD component.
<br />

<br />
